		"claim a durable outpost": "占住稳固前哨",
		"improve the bishop against the pawn chain": "让象更契合兵链",
		"improve the knight's long-term square": "改善马的长期据点",
		"steer toward a comfortable endgame": "引向更舒服的残局",
		"It secures a healthier pawn structure, with fewer long-term pawn weaknesses.": "它让兵形更健康，长期兵弱点也更少。",
		"It plants a knight on a durable outpost at {square}, using a weak square the pawns cannot easily challenge.": "它把马安在 {square} 的稳固前哨上，利用了一个兵很难再驱赶的弱格。",
